    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>1 Peking duck (about 5-6 pounds)</li>
            <li>1/4 cup hoisin sauce</li>
            <li>2 tablespoons soy sauce</li>
            <li>1 tablespoon rice vinegar</li>
            <li>1 tablespoon honey</li>
            <li>1 teaspoon sesame oil</li>
            <li>1 teaspoon five-spice powder</li>
            <li>1 bunch green onions, sliced</li>
            <li>16-20 Mandarin pancakes (store-bought or homemade)</li>
            <li>Cucumber strips and sliced green onions for garnish</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Tags</h2>
